title: Provides that a lien filed by the crime victim's board shall have no negative impact on the victim's consumer credit rating or application for credit
summary: Provides that a lien filed by the crime victim's board shall have no negative impact on the victim's consumer credit rating or application for credit.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law, in relation to prohibiting any negative impact on a crime victim's credit rating from a lien created under section 634 of such law
